            "title": "An International, Multicentre, Randomised, Open, Controlled, Two-parallel Group, Phase II Pilot Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of ARIXTRA™ for Anticoagulation of Patients With Atrial Fibrillation Undergoing Electric Cardioversion Following Transesophageal Echocardiography",
